name: WALsome3D
description:
Heyyah!! We are the Design Squad from West Agile Labs (WAL).


We are young, we are agile and we are super proud to model, render and share WALsome 3D, free to use 3D shapes kit for the design community out there.


We have crafted a total of 176 components, 16 shapes that come in 3 different materials to choose from :

Plastic - Rendered in 7 Colors

Metal - Rendered in 3 Colors

Glass - Rendered in 1 Color


We would love to see what you create with these shapes.
